            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Less accurate since Apple's Mail Privacy Protection (2021), which pre-fetches images and inflates open rates by 5-15% for Apple Mail users. Use click-through rate as the primary engagement metric and treat opens as a directional signal.</p></div></div>
